<h1>TreeHouse</h1>
<p>TreeHouse displays data about <a href='http://forrst.com'>Forrst</a> users.</p>
<p>Unlike <a href='http://forrst.me/kyle'>forrst.me</a>, which only has links to the services the user has accounts on (e.g. GitHub, Facebook, etc.), Tree House displays the most useful info from those services. For example, if the user has a GitHub account, their repositories are listed.</p>
<p><a href='kyle'>Check it out yourself!</a><br/>(If you've got a Forrst account, just add your username on to the url in your address bar.)</p>
